		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />A couple years ago when I wrote a GBA game, I did exactly what tepples described above. Used the two channels directly, one for music and one for sfx. I didn't want to write a mixer, the free-for-commercial-use ones didn't compile or straight crashed at runtime, and the ones that worked required payment.

		

