	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Sega CD accessory could have only a small amount of data loaded at once: about 6 Mbit. Anything more than that<br /><br />LOADING<br /><br />usually required gameplay to freeze for a couple seconds. The FDS had the same problem.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
